<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">בּהמה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
בּהמה / behêmâh / be-hay-maw'

===Etymology===
From an unused root (probably meaning to be mute); 

===Noun===
'''בּהמה'''

# properly a dumb beast; especially any large quadruped or animal (often collectively): - [[beast]], [[cattle]].

